					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is the kind of article I would really love to see more often. It offers a perfect combination of horror (spiders entering your bloodstream), ridiculous nonsense (a hospital run by invertebrates in tiny labcoats) and warm feelings (I hate bugs, yet I do feel sorry for the poor critters). Great one.</p> 
