				<wikidot:authorName>Jacob Conwell</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1372582</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Holy hell, you guys got this one up quick. Roget releasing two collabs, Zyn doing a solo article, what bizarro world is this?</p> <p>In all seriousness, this one is a delightful mix of creepy and tragic. On one hand, the idea of spiders literally entering your body to attempt surgery is pure horror. On the other hand, the fact that the poor little staff worked themselves to death attempting to help others tugs on my hearstrings.</p> <p>Either way, this is a nice article. Enthusiastic +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
